# This MVP uses OpenStreetMap, Nominatim, and OSRM without an API key.
#
# Shared trip links need a persistent key-value database in production.
# Add an Upstash Redis integration from the Vercel Marketplace and connect
# these env vars to the Vercel project. Local development falls back to .data.
# KV_REST_API_URL=
# KV_REST_API_TOKEN=
#
# If your integration exposes Upstash-native names instead, those work too:
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
